{"id":563657,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/【立此存照】ab站血洗日剧欧美剧/","date":"2017-07-13T01:29:10Z","modified":"2017-07-13T01:32:11Z","title":"【立此存照】AB站血洗日剧欧美剧专区","content":"<div id=\"attachment_563676\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-563676\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签.jpg 1350w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签-300x186.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签-768x476.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/B站热门标签-1024x634.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">B站电视剧热门标签被删得只剩“国产”剧；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://zx.sina.cn/f/2017-07-13/zx-ifyiakwa3970203.d.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">新浪科技｜AB站又一批影视作品下架 A站影视区全部消失</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>7月12日晚间开始，陆续有A站和B站用户发现大量影视内容视频从网站上下架。</p>\n<p>从目前的情况来看，A站的影视区已经全部消失，即电影、电视剧等内容被彻底清空。</p>\n<p>B站的情况似乎稍好一些，根据《好奇心日报》的不完全统计，外国影视内容是重灾区。与此同时，也有包括《我的团长我的团》、李少红版《红楼梦》在内的一批国产剧被下架。而动画、纪录片、用户自主上传的自制短视频节目等其他栏目，总体上来看虽然也有部分下架，但影响并不是太大。</p>\n<p>[&#8230;]不过，目前B站上仍有大量没有版权的纪录片、综艺可以正常收看。</p>\n<p>[&#8230;]无论此次事件是由于版权引起，还是政府加强对于娱乐业的监管，消费者在互联网上的娱乐方式正在变得越来越少。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>以下图片来自新浪微博 <a href=\"http://weibo.com/1043320390/Fc9yg0bEF\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@半岛晨报</a>： </strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44ia6ij20c80lpjsz.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563659\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44ia6ij20c80lpjsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44ia6ij20c80lpjsz.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44ia6ij20c80lpjsz-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44npdgj20c80d70sp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563660\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44npdgj20c80d70sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44npdgj20c80d70sp.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy44npdgj20c80d70sp-278x300.jpg 278w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy450absj20c80lrq4c.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563664\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy450absj20c80lrq4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy450absj20c80lrq4c.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy450absj20c80lrq4c-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy455al3j20c80lrtab.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563665\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy455al3j20c80lrtab.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy455al3j20c80lrtab.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy455al3j20c80lrtab-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy45czqzj20c80lqjtd.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563661\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/3e2fce46ly1fhhy45c